# Gitignore for Qt and Visual Studio Projects
# Worksheet 6

# Build artifacts (recursive covers any subfolder)
**/build/
**/Debug/
**/Release/
**/RelWithDebInfo/
**/x64/
**/out/
**/CMakeFiles/
**/ws6_autogen/
**/*.dir/
**/*.log
**/*.stamp
**/*.tlog
**/*.idb
**/*.pdb
**/*.obj
**/*.exe
**/*.dll
**/*.lib

# Visual Studio / QtCreator Junk
**/.vs/
**/.qt/
**/.qtcreator/
**/*.vcxproj
**/*.vcxproj.filters
**/*.vcxproj.user
**/*.sln
**/*.slnx
**/*.autosave
**/CMakeCache.txt
**/cmake_install.cmake
**/CMakeSettings.json

# User specific project settings
*.user
*.suo
*.userosscache
*.sln.docstates

# Worksheet artifacts
# (Ignoring the PDF in the repo to keep it small)
Worksheet6_v1.pdf
